These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Food: pear, grapefruit, spinach, plum
Hobby: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. Food:grapefruit is between Food:pear and Hobby:gardening##2
2. Food:grapefruit is on the left or right of Hobby:board-games##3
3. Food:grapefruit is somewhere between Food:plum and Food:pear##7
4. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
5. Food:plum is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
6. Hobby:gardening is somewhere to the left of Hobby:board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Food   | spinach | plum       | grapefruit | pear        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

