Food: avocado, potato, eggplant, asparagus
1. Food:asparagus is somewhere between Food:eggplant and Pet:hedgehog##7
2. Pet:snake is somewhere to the left of Pet:dog##5
3. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Food:asparagus##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Food:asparagus is between Food:eggplant and Food:potato##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Food   | potato   | asparagus | eggplant | avocado |

