.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Game: backgammon, monopoly, canasta, billiard
Sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. Game:backgammon is somewhere between Sport:golf and Game:billiard##7
3. Game:canasta == Sport:volleyball##1
4. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1
5. Game:monopoly is on the left of Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon | billiard       | canasta |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

